    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Ephi</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>How come its cold in here </l>
          <l>Even when it's summer time </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>As for you </l>
          <l>That's your last stop </l>
          <l>It's time to say good bye, </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>How come its raining </l>
          <l>And the sky is blue and clear </l>
          <l>How come you're smiling </l>
          <l>When it's so so sad here </l>
          <l>It's a standard cliche, but damn so true </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>It was supposed to be a happy song, you changed the plan </l>
          <l>Some people were meant to live </l>
          <l>But you had to rather give </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>the leaves are falling well its mid December after all </l>
          <l>They seem so peaceful there </l>
          <l>Fading away disappearing </l>
          <l>Good bye my friend </l>
          <l>Fair well take care </l>
          <l>I'll see you when I die</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
